    <item>
      <title>先锋创纪录的降费举措收紧了贝莱德和景顺的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vanguard-s-record-fee-cuts-tighten-screws-on-blackrock-invesco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团 (Vanguard Group Inc.) 为降低投资大众的费用而采取的迄今为止最大的举措，让行业竞争对手面临一个痛苦的选择。要么效仿，可能损失数亿美元收入 — — 要么坚守阵地，冒着失去急需的市场份额的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vanguard-s-record-fee-cuts-tighten-screws-on-blackrock-invesco</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰通过发行美元债券重新加入区域外汇债务热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/poland-re-enters-regional-fx-debt-rush-with-dollar-bond-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰在短短几个月内第二次重返国际市场，出售以美元计价的债券，以满足创纪录的融资需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/poland-re-enters-regional-fx-debt-rush-with-dollar-bond-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:43:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席巴尔金谈政策不确定性和利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-barkin-on-policy-uncertainty-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士满联邦储备银行行长托马斯·巴金 (Thomas Barkin) 讨论了需要更多时间来了解美国经济和通胀走向的必要性，因为特朗普总统的政策存在高度不确定性，而且他认为利率“适度限制”。他在“彭博监测”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/fed-s-barkin-on-policy-uncertainty-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:39:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其加入新兴市场债券热潮，2025 年首次发行美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/turkey-joining-em-bond-rush-with-first-dollar-sale-of-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其正在发售今年首笔以美元计价的债券，该国政府希望在新兴市场债券销售繁忙的一周中锁定低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/turkey-joining-em-bond-rush-with-first-dollar-sale-of-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部将拍卖 1250 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/treasury-to-sell-125-billion-in-debt-at-auction-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部将在下周的季度再融资拍卖中出售 1250 亿美元债券。长期债券销售指导保持不变。美国贸易逆差也飙升至 980 亿美元。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/treasury-to-sell-125-billion-in-debt-at-auction-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长莱恩表示，通胀风险下需要灵活调整利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/ecb-lane-says-agility-needed-on-rates-amid-inflation-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，由于通胀风险仍然存在，欧洲央行应保持灵活的货币政策制定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/ecb-lane-says-agility-needed-on-rates-amid-inflation-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦将加强对俄罗斯影子舰队油轮的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/denmark-to-intensify-scrutiny-of-russia-s-shadow-fleet-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦将加强对通过其狭窄海峡运输俄罗斯石油的船只的检查，以保护环境和海上安全，免受莫斯科影子舰队中老旧船只的侵害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/denmark-to-intensify-scrutiny-of-russia-s-shadow-fleet-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战加剧不确定性 邦吉预计利润将缩水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bunge-sees-full-year-profits-shrinking-to-lowest-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的贸易战加剧了农作物市场的不确定性，邦吉全球公司预计今年的利润将缩水至疫情爆发前的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bunge-sees-full-year-profits-shrinking-to-lowest-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 11:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战担忧压倒特朗普对伊朗施压 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国和中国之间的贸易战将损害全球经济增长，压倒了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大对欧佩克成员国伊朗经济压力的计划，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：服务业数据疲软，科技股受创，债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 和 Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 的业绩表现不佳，再次引发人们对科技行业在人工智能领域投入的数十亿美元何时才能开始获得回报的担忧，导致股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 22:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
